      "q": "Is this matrimony platform free to use?",
      "a": "Yes. You can create a profile, browse matches, and use basic features for free. Premium features unlock advanced filters and unlimited interactions."
    },
    {
      "q": "How do I create my profile?",
      "a": "Simply sign up with your basic details, complete your profile by adding personal and family information, upload a photo, and start exploring suitable matches."
    },
    {
      "q": "Can I edit my profile after registration?",
      "a": "Yes. You can update your profile details, preferences, photos, and other information anytime from your account settings."
    },
    {
      "q": "Can I shortlist profiles for later?",
      "a": "Yes. You can add profiles to your shortlist and access them anytime from your account."
    }
